{"tid":274114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"T.O.P@BIGBANG仍昏迷戴氧氣罩　母親含淚反駁警察　指情況不樂觀","createTime":"2017-06-07T05:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T12:46:56.000Z","uid":66943,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e2bbf7650068fe6dd8383d042216d31009f72c5","tid":274114,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:40:40.000Z","msg":"BIGBANG成員T.O.P（崔勝鉉）昨日因為服用過量藥物暈倒，被緊急送入ICU治理，昨日警方對外發布消息，指T.O.P生命並沒有危險，又否認他失去意識，只是睡着的狀態，等到藥物效用過後就會甦醒。不過，一直陪伴在T.O.P身旁的母親今日早上走出ICU對記者表示兒子的狀態非常不好，含着淚反駁警方「因為安眠藥而睡着」的說法！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/624977/xlarge/36629e6261d77b0f8f80f03aa3ab9df8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F624977%2Fxlarge%2F36629e6261d77b0f8f80f03aa3ab9df8.jpg&h=0b523c37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nT.O.P母親親自向記者哭訴，指警方的講法不合理，而T.O.P現在仍是昏迷中，情況並不樂觀。（網上圖片）<br />\nT.O.P所屬公司YG娛樂的相關人士亦表示，T.O.P的媽媽對於警方的講法十分生氣，並指T.O.P現在要戴着氧氣罩，依然是昏迷的狀態，認為警方的說法荒唐至極！而基於探訪的限制，現時只有T.O.P媽媽和幾名家人守候在側，由於未知道T.O.P有否出現過缺氧，所以即使他醒來，也是令人擔憂的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/625016/xlarge/c02eaf05ae5b627994ee3cfdde26c025.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F625016%2Fxlarge%2Fc02eaf05ae5b627994ee3cfdde26c025.jpg&h=4973b357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有韓媒拍得T.O.P母親離開時忍不住落淚。（網上圖片）<br />\n另外，今日韓國時間下午4時（約香港時間下午3時），T.O.P留醫中的梨大木洞醫院會召開記者會，據知會由院長直接交代關於T.O.P的病情，但到底會透露多少、警察會否參與，都仍是未知之數。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/624978/xlarge/41911c61a65b68a659b8cf9fe76b6dcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F624978%2Fxlarge%2F41911c61a65b68a659b8cf9fe76b6dcd.jpg&h=ac3d36d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://replygif.net/i/154.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Freplygif.net%2Fi%2F154.gif&h=c20b1814&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c6a731fad4d2cbcef9007e03f203ea150bcde39","tid":274114,"uid":2423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8628f3ad10ed61cfe7c7e2595da9ca30c7b1b2","tid":274114,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:42:23.000Z","msg":"邊撚個話？"},{"pid":"962b051b01faaf0d2726deab5c69d9f950b234ca","tid":274114,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:43:26.000Z","msg":"有咁耐風流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d892691c7cb65a9ebc2f1adaf8c1b78ab14f8f68","tid":274114,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:43:44.000Z","msg":"唔識"},{"pid":"451c8573443e01badf89eb6b239099baf0839d51","tid":274114,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252164774109ae3bbd81590a89ae5a0a581b3e3f","tid":274114,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:46:30.000Z","msg":"韓狗早死早著啦"},{"pid":"64ef4c6320017ce91dd8adbed592c2337fabc848","tid":274114,"uid":40735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4865e3e08315238d86f9003cb77d57b55fc46e5","tid":274114,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e826e2f2a07168f9159f182957a3a0459600571","tid":274114,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:50:09.000Z","msg":"佢阿媽識春咩<br />\n<br />\n用氧氣罩即係識自己抖氣啦"},{"pid":"d49c2040e33523763d6e2242f79dfcf534bf36a5","tid":274114,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T12:46:56.000Z","msg":"唔洗再有少女買演唱會飛受騙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n短期內都開唔到演唱會。"}]}